@startuml adapter_before
title Adapter Pattern - BEFORE (Current State)
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam classBackgroundColor #FFE4E1

class CreditCard {
    - double amount
    - String number
    - Date date
    - String cvv
    - boolean valid
    + isValid(): boolean
    + getAmount(): double
    + setAmount(double): void
}

class Paypal {
    + {static} Map<String,String> DATA_BASE
}

class FlightOrder {
    + processOrderWithCreditCard(CreditCard): boolean
    + processOrderWithPayPal(String, String): boolean
    + payWithCreditCard(CreditCard, double): boolean
    + payWithPayPal(String, String, double): boolean
}

FlightOrder --> CreditCard: uses
FlightOrder --> Paypal: uses

note bottom of FlightOrder
  Incompatible interfaces:
  - CreditCard: isValid(), getAmount()
  - PayPal: static DATA_BASE + email/password
  
  Duplicate payment processing code
  Different method signatures
  Hard to add new payment methods
end note

@enduml
